<Base
  title="How Long Does Email Warm-Up Take? Realistic Timelines by Volume Target"
  description="Email warm-up takes 2–4 weeks for most cold email volumes: 10–20 sends/day in week 1, ramping to 50–100/day by weeks 3–4. New domains, higher targets, and poor engagement stretch the timeline."
